flowchart TD
    Start([Trigger: Admin klik Generate Rules<br>atau Cronjob Bulanan])

    Start --> SetParams[Set parameter:<br>min_support, min_confidence,<br>min_transactions]
    SetParams --> Truncate[Truncate apriori_rules table]

    Truncate --> FetchData[Fetch data transaksi:<br>order_items dari orders completed]
    FetchData --> DataOK{"Data cukup?<br>&gt;= min_transactions"}

    DataOK -->|Tidak| Fallback["Cold-start fallback<br>Best Seller / Admin Picks"]
    DataOK -->|Ya| BuildMatrix["Bangun transaction matrix:<br>user_id / session_id to products"]

    BuildMatrix --> RunApriori["AprioriService::mine()"]
    RunApriori --> PyScript["shell_exec: python mine.py"]
    PyScript --> PyOutput["Python output: JSON rules<br>support, confidence, lift"]

    PyOutput --> ParseJSON[Parse JSON rules]
    ParseJSON --> FilterLift{"Filter: Lift &gt; 1?"}
    FilterLift -->|Tidak| SkipRule[Skip rule]
    FilterLift -->|Ya| InsertDB[Insert ke apriori_rules:<br>antecedent, consequent,<br>support, confidence, lift]

    InsertDB --> MoreRules{Ada rules lain?}
    MoreRules -->|Ya| FilterLift
    MoreRules -->|Tidak| Done

    SkipRule --> MoreRules
    Fallback --> Done

    Done --> Notify([Redirect ke Apriori<br>refresh halaman])


